can we change instance type without down time?

Single EC2:
  ❌ needs downtime
  stop → change → start

ASG + Instance Refresh:
  ✅ zero downtime
  rolling update
  ALB routes to healthy instances

ASG + Blue/Green:
  ✅ zero downtime
  instant rollback
  more resources needed

Best practice for prod:
  ✅ always use ASG
  ✅ instance refresh
  ✅ min healthy 50%+

