Launch Template = Complete EC2 Definition

Launch Template
├── AMI              → OS + software (image)
├── Instance Type    → CPU + RAM
├── EBS              → disk storage
├── Key Pair         → SSH access
├── Security Group   → firewall rules
├── IAM Role         → AWS permissions
├── User Data        → startup script
└── Network          → VPC + subnet

--------------

AMI           = image  ✅
              → what OS
              → what software pre-installed
              → Amazon Linux, Ubuntu, Windows

Instance Type = CPU + RAM ✅
              → t3.micro  = 1 CPU  1 GB RAM
              → t3.medium = 2 CPU  4 GB RAM
              → t3.large  = 2 CPU  8 GB RAM

EBS           = disk ✅
              → how much storage
              → gp3, io2, etc
              → 8 GB, 20 GB, 100 GB

